OL,3,CGas pipework at Royal Maternity
OL,4,CHospital to cost #50k to repair
OL,6,FA medical gas pipework issue at
OL,7,FBelfast's new maternity hospital will
OL,8,Fcost approximately #50,000 to fix,
OL,9,FHealth Minister Mike Nesbitt has said.
OL,11,FIn a written statement to the Northern
OL,12,FIreland Assembly, Mr Nesbitt said he
OL,13,Fhad been assured the problem would be
OL,14,Fsorted "as swiftly as possible" and
OL,15,Fwould not further delay the project.
OL,17,FWhen he revealed the issue to MLAs
OL,18,Flast week, Mr Nesbitt described it as
OL,19,F"totally shocking".
