OL,6,FThe hospital, at the Royal Victoria
OL,7,Fsite, is already almost 10 years
OL,8,Fbehind schedule after numerous delays,
OL,9,Fbut it was hoped it would finally open
OL,10,Fnext year.
OL,12,FHowever, after the Belfast Trust took
OL,13,Fpossession of the new building in
OL,14,FMarch, testing of its water systems
OL,15,Fshowed high levels of the bacteria
OL,16,FPseudomonas aeruginosa (PsA), leading
OL,17,Fthe trust to say the project was
OL,18,Ffacing a significant new delay.
