OL,6,FDuring a debate in the Assembly, Mr
OL,7,FNesbitt raised that another problem
OL,8,Fhad been identified, this time with
OL,9,Fthe medical gas pipework.
OL,11,FProviding an update on Wednesday, he
OL,12,Fsaid he knew MLAs shared his concerns
OL,13,Fabout the new hospital.
OL,15,FHe added: "I am advised that the
OL,16,Fmedical gas pipe issue was raised by
OL,17,FBelfast Trust in November 2023 as part
OL,18,Fof the contractual handover process
OL,19,Ffor the building.
