OL,6,F"It was detailed in the handover
OL,7,Fdocumentation as a 'caveat', which is
OL,8,Fin essence a defect which was known at
OL,9,Fthe point of handover.
OL,11,F"In recent days I have again met the
OL,12,Ftrust and it has assured me the issue
OL,13,Fwith the medical gas pipework will be
OL,14,Fremedied as swiftly as possible.
OL,16,F"I have been advised the cost to
OL,17,Fresolve the issue will be
OL,18,Fapproximately #50,000."
