OL,6,FMr Nesbitt added: "Although the defect
OL,7,Fhad been identified for some time, the
OL,8,FBelfast Trust and departmental
OL,9,Fofficials had only recently received a
OL,10,Freport into the options for correcting
OL,11,Fthe problem.
OL,13,F"I have been informed that the work
OL,14,Fgoing on in parallel to test the water
OL,15,Fsystems regrettably, but unavoidably,
OL,16,Fcontributed to the delay in the
OL,17,Fproduction of this report.
