OL,6,F"The trust has advised that they will
OL,7,Fwork to ensure that the issue is fixed
OL,8,Fas quickly as possible and that it
OL,9,Fwill not add any further to the delays
OL,10,Fwhich I know members are rightly
OL,11,Fconcerned about.
OL,13,F"While my frustrations remain, the
OL,14,Fprimary focus must be on
OL,15,Fsatisfactorily resolving the water
OL,16,Fsupply issues and securing the opening
OL,17,Fof the new maternity hospital as
OL,18,Fexpeditiously as possible."
OL,20,FThe new hospital is years overdue and
OL,21,Fwell over budget.
